WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:07.898
Hey, good morning family, how are y'all doing today? Well, I have some things on my heart that the Lord has shown me, and I'm excited about this.

00:00:07.899 --> 00:00:21.839
He started talking to me about the outpouring of His Spirit again—a major change coming, a major—I'm going to say it's like the tipping of the waterfall again.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:44.243
And the things that the Lord is talking to me about, I saw a door, a massive door, and it was a white door, a beautiful painted white door, but on this door there was purple, there were swirls of different—like the glory of what I want to call the Shekinah Glory.

00:00:44.244 --> 00:00:49.639
It looked like mist, and it was covering this door, but it was beautiful.

00:00:49.640 --> 00:01:00.398
The colors, the pinks and stuff, the clouds are in front of it and behind. In the door frame behind the door was like a dimension.

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:12.787
Okay, and in that dimension behind it was the glory, and I could see the light coming through the cracks of the door.

00:01:12.788 --> 00:01:23.299
It was shining through that door on the cracks, and I could see like it was just trying to bust through—the glory of God was trying to bust through this door.

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:32.319
And behind it was the same, which was amazing. I don't know how else to describe this.

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:42.226
Behind it was the same dimension as the front side, but it was like a door that was standing all alone, but it was a door that you could open up to it.

00:01:42.227 --> 00:01:58.118
And I had to say it like this, but this is a way I can try—I'm trying to paint a picture for y'all like The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe, how there was a closet and they walked through the closet and they could go through the other dimension into Narnia.

00:01:58.119 --> 00:02:09.806
So that's kind of like what I saw. It was a door that was like a passage, but on the other side of it, without opening the door, He was walking through the dimension.

00:02:09.807 --> 00:02:16.423
It was still in the same dimension because on this side I could see the pink and all the beautiful stuff again.

00:02:16.424 --> 00:02:30.559
But the Lord said to me, 'Everything is about to change, for in this space of time you've hit this where we are.'Help me, Holy Spirit.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:39.559
He said, 'This dispensation of time is coming to an end.'That's what He was saying to me and where we are in it.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:51.281
And I saw Adam's lease coming up again. It was up, and we were going into another space of time.

00:02:51.282 --> 00:03:12.978
And He said to me, during Rosh Hashanah this week—this week is an amazing week because this is the beginning on the second, which is in two days, the beginning of Rosh Hashanah, which goes into the third and I believe the fourth, at whenever the new moon and all that is.

00:03:12.979 --> 00:03:19.199
I believe—I'm not going to quote right because I am not a Jewish scholar—but I'm just saying this is what I've seen.

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:46.000
So He said, 'This time frame is the beginning of the new creative miracles, that we have hit a time and space that we've hit a time in history where Adam's lease is coming up, that we are getting ready for the great outpouring and we're going home.'We're getting ready to go home.

00:03:46.001 --> 00:03:56.861
I saw the glory behind this door and I saw the door was going to open. And He said, 'In a 24-hour period, everything will change.

00:03:56.862 --> 00:04:31.490
Everything that you know, everything that you've ever known up until this point in human history, everything will change like a light switch.'He said, 'Brandon, it's going to be like a light switch that flips on.'He said that time frame is coming to an end, what we've seen, and He said, 'You're coming into a new time frame, and you're going to cross and you're going to go through this door.'And I saw the glory again upon the bride, upon the body, in a way that is huge.

00:04:31.491 --> 00:04:44.057
We think we've seen stuff in the past—revivals, demonstrations, and manifestations of the glory, outpourings of when Azusa Street happened.

00:04:44.058 --> 00:05:03.847
You know, there was a prophetic word that was given over a hundred years ago now that said that there would be another revival like Azusa in a hundred years that would be bigger than what happened at Azusa, and it's been going on 120-some years now.

00:05:03.848 --> 00:05:09.340
But He said they didn't quite say it was going to be a hundred years, it would be in a hundred-year time frame.

00:05:09.341 --> 00:05:17.889
Well, we're in 120 years. In two years, I believe, we're in that time frame of that prophetic word that was given.

00:05:17.890 --> 00:05:30.936
So here we are at the last of the last. I'm telling you all, Jesus is coming and the sun is going down on this dispensation of grace.

00:05:30.937 --> 00:05:42.296
And I saw the devil petitioning again for his seven-year tribulation. And I saw he had a—this time he had a black cloak on.

00:05:42.296 --> 00:05:49.562
It was a massive black cloak, and he was moving around very sneaky and just evil, the way he was moving.

00:05:49.563 --> 00:05:59.461
And he is lurching around, kind of like Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs whenever that old witch was there and she had that black cloak on. That's the way the devil looked.

00:05:59.462 --> 00:06:14.351
But he was going and I saw him go and he was talking to the Pope, which I think is just a wow, but he was talking to the Pope, influencing the Vatican and the church in Rome.

00:06:14.352 --> 00:06:23.097
Because I was like, 'What is that all about?'But I saw the devil trying to go and influence and talk to the Pope in the Vatican and he was speaking to him.

00:06:23.098 --> 00:06:26.832
I don't even know if the Pope knew he was being talked to, but he was.

00:06:26.833 --> 00:06:38.275
He was talking to the Pope, and I saw the Pope and he had his white beanie on—his head thing—and he was looking down.

00:06:38.276 --> 00:06:43.345
But the devils were standing behind him trying to influence him, talking to him.

00:06:43.346 --> 00:06:54.152
And then I saw Italy and I saw cracks all in the soil again with like lava and fire all over Italy again.

00:06:54.153 --> 00:06:59.472
I saw fire and it was like the earth was splitting, like from an earthquake, remember?

00:06:59.473 --> 00:07:11.872
And I warned you all about a volcano that the Lord told me to intercede in behalf of Italy, that there would be a lot of people perish because of a tsunami in the water and because of volcanic activity.

00:07:11.873 --> 00:07:20.667
I told you this about a year ago. And when I was interceding, I saw the angels coming out of the sky and they were warning the people and waking them up.

00:07:20.668 --> 00:07:33.208
And there was a mist, like a canary in the coal mine. I told you all about the canary in the coal mine and it was on the perch and it fell over dead, and there was a gas coming up out of the ground.

00:07:33.209 --> 00:07:40.889
And I saw like a mist, a fog over the land over this town in Italy, and it was on the coastline.

00:07:40.890 --> 00:07:49.244
And the angels were warning the people and they were coming out, and I saw a portal open up over Italy.

00:07:49.245 --> 00:08:00.705
If anybody who's followed this channel for a while remembers this, that I warned about this and we were interceding for Italy that this major earthquake would not take place and destroy a lot of people.

00:08:00.706 --> 00:08:14.453
I saw 300,000 people perish. And so I saw that again. I saw Italy splitting open, I saw fire coming up out of these cracks, and I thought it was interesting.

00:08:14.454 --> 00:08:22.386
But I saw the Pope being influenced by a demon, by the devil, and he was talking to the devil.

00:08:22.387 --> 00:08:58.380
And so I saw in this time frame where we are in eternity and the Lord was telling me, He said, 'Brandon, we are at that sliver of time.'And He said, 'And you know when the Bible says a day is a thousand years to the Lord, a thousand years is as a day, right?'So I saw thousand, thousand, thousand, thousand—clear to the beginning of time the Lord showed me.

00:08:58.381 --> 00:09:10.608
And I'm telling you, I had an experience of the Lord beyond anything I've been able to ever tell you all, and I've told you all some amazing experiences.

00:09:10.609 --> 00:09:19.074
But this experience that I had with the Lord was beyond anything I've ever seen before.

00:09:19.075 --> 00:09:29.188
It was like—to say it shook me—it was beyond saying it. My son and my wife, they recorded it; they were here for it.

00:09:29.189 --> 00:09:46.199
And I'm not going to go into a lot of it because a lot of the word that was given when I had this visitation about four or five days ago was so intense because He was speaking to me directly. And so a lot of it is not for the public.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:10:07.635
But in this, He showed me Adam's lease, He showed me the door like I'm talking about, He showed me where we are in time again, and He took time on a thin line, a thread, and He spread it out by every thousand years.

00:10:07.636 --> 00:10:18.253
And He took me through time and it was way out there, but I could see from the beginning whenever He spoke the world into existence.

00:10:18.254 --> 00:10:26.824
I saw Adam walking the earth, I saw Noah and the flood. He took me to each one and how they were milestones in history.

00:10:26.825 --> 00:10:36.553
And I saw each thing, from the Roman Empire to the Ottoman Empire, He showed it to me.

00:10:36.554 --> 00:10:44.986
But each thing was divided up into a thousand years, and then a thousand years would divide up into a hundred years, and then it went down to ten years, to a decade.

00:10:44.987 --> 00:10:56.080
And He showed it out, it was on a timeline. And He took me through the timeline in space with Him, traveling to where we are right now, ladies and gentlemen.

00:10:56.081 --> 00:11:07.952
And I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is getting ready to come back, and He's coming back for not a busted and disgusted church, He's coming back for a glorious church.

00:11:07.953 --> 00:11:14.492
He's coming back for a church that's on fire for Him. He is looking and yearning for His bride.

00:11:14.493 --> 00:11:26.871
And I'm telling you, it's time to get more serious than you've ever been before, for where we are in time—time is up, one last call.

00:11:26.872 --> 00:11:53.587
He said, 'Remember, where we are right now,'He said, 'Brandon, I can control time.'And He showed me where Adam's lease and everything was up, but there was a sliver right here in between, like a couple of seconds, like a couple minutes—you know what I'm saying—like it was a long enough time for Him to have His revival and be able to bring in a harvest of souls.

00:11:53.588 --> 00:12:19.560
He said, 'Because I have never been defeated nor will I ever be.'He said, 'I will not allow you to run back and be afraid of what the devil is doing.'He said, 'You are to put on your armor and be strong in the Lord in the power of His might.'It's time for us to be like the Davids.

00:12:19.561 --> 00:12:28.599
And He said, 'There's a lot of people, Brandon, that are tired—the older generation, they're tired and they're ready to come home.'And He said, 'Allow that to happen.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:35.130
If they're ready and they want to come home and they're satisfied, they can come on home.

00:12:35.131 --> 00:12:53.662
But I will not allow my church to be defeated.'He said, 'They will be victorious on the way out.'He said, 'The seeds that you've sowed in the past will come to harvest at last.'And He said, 'That's not even about the bad seeds, Brandon, that the wicked have sowed.'He said, 'I'm a God of the harvest.

00:12:53.663 --> 00:12:57.246
I'm going to bring in financial harvest beyond anything you can comprehend.

00:12:57.247 --> 00:13:27.457
There will be decamillionaires in the near future.'He said, 'Brandon, there will be a transfer of the wealth from the wicked like it was when the children of Israel left Egypt.'He said, 'I will bring forth a harvest of finances on my children as a sign and a wonder in these last days.'I saw a group of people rising up that were—and I didn't even know what the word decamillionaire was.

00:13:27.457 --> 00:13:34.797
I'm telling y'all, I'm not a real educated person, and I had told my wife, 'This is what the Lord used.'I said, 'He said decamillionaire.

00:13:34.798 --> 00:13:52.070
What is a decamillionaire?'I said, 'Can we Google it?'So she Googled it and said, 'Honey, it's above ten million dollars.'Anybody who has above a ten million dollar—the Lord said that there is tons of seed in the ground that's coming to pass and there's harvest that's coming for His bright people.

00:13:52.071 --> 00:14:00.534
He has not forgotten those seeds; those seeds have lied dormant in the ground and they're going to spring forth now.

00:14:00.534 --> 00:14:11.753
It's time for the seeds that you sowed—financial, sacrificial seeds—that God said, 'I'm going to breathe on those seeds and I'm going to bring a harvest to you now.'It's time.

00:14:11.754 --> 00:14:17.290
He said, 'Brandon, do not let go of the seeds you've sacrificially sowed.

00:14:17.291 --> 00:14:34.960
Do not let go of the sacrificial time that you've given.'He said, 'Brandon, I'm bringing forth great joy, I'm bringing forth great harvest.'He said, 'Days of Heaven on Earth, fun days are coming for my body.

00:14:34.961 --> 00:14:42.159
It's not a time to be woe-is-me. Oh gosh, we got to go and hide in the caves.

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:52.734
It's time to rise and shine for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.'And I'm telling you, the Lord showed me a financial harvest.

00:14:52.735 --> 00:14:59.010
People ask, 'Why do we need that if we're going to heaven?'If you don't want yours, I'll take it for you.

00:14:59.011 --> 00:15:06.887
If you don't want your financial harvest and what God's wanting to do for you, that's fine; just put it all over there and give it to somebody who will use it for Him.

00:15:06.888 --> 00:15:13.689
You know, people get all bent out of shape, 'Well, I don't want to do—I want to just go to heaven.'We're going to go victorious.

00:15:13.690 --> 00:15:20.057
We're going to go with our heads held high. We're not cowering down because the devil's taking ground.

00:15:20.058 --> 00:15:37.998
He said, 'Brandon, the problem is that the body of Christ has been off-kilter.'He said, 'They've tried to demasculinize the men of the church by making them metrosexual, feminine like'—He called them limp-wristed.

00:15:37.999 --> 00:15:51.879
He said, 'It's time for my men to get a backbone like David did in the Bible, and they're mighty men of war.'And He said, 'If you want to take the land, son, you've got to have some testosterone to you.

00:15:51.880 --> 00:16:03.500
You've got to have some manpower behind you. You can't be this passive, seeker-friendly—well, you know, whatever will be, will be.'He said, 'You've got to be a warrior in the Kingdom.

00:16:03.501 --> 00:16:12.818
You've got to take your sword and your shield like David did and go and take the land.'You know, He showed me, He said how it was with Moses.

00:16:12.819 --> 00:16:24.928
They said to Joshua and Caleb, 'The giants make us like grasshoppers,'and they had a whole generation die off before they were able to do something.

00:16:24.929 --> 00:16:42.239
And He said, 'Brandon, if I have to do that again, I can do it. But I know there is a generation—I'm talking about us—we're not going to have to pass it and let a lot of people go home like they did in forty years. We don't have forty years, ladies and gentlemen.

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:59.634
Jesus is coming.'But it was just an illustration of what He's talking about—raising up Davids, raising up the ones that would take the land and taking the land back for Him, being bold about our faith, being bold about laying hands on the sick and casting out devils.

00:16:59.635 --> 00:17:08.860
Freely we've been given, freely we give it out, sharing the good news with the people for this last harvest.

00:17:08.861 --> 00:17:27.838
And if Jesus Christ could come back tomorrow, I'm just saying—you know, I'm always expecting—but go with your head held high, go with a fight to you, have a backbone about who you are and take the land for Jesus.

00:17:27.839 --> 00:17:34.092
That's what I'm talking about. And that's what He showed me, that He never designed us for fear.

00:17:34.093 --> 00:17:56.688
And He said to me, 'Where in my word have you ever heard me tell you to be afraid of what's coming?'He said, 'Never.'In Joshua 1:9, He said to me, 'Be strong and of good courage, for I the Lord your God am with you wherever you go.'Now, I may have not said that exactly right, but you can look it up yourself.

00:17:56.689 --> 00:18:10.557
But I'm just saying, He was saying, 'I want you not to be afraid.'He said, 'Brandon, there is a shaking coming, there is a storm that is coming upon your shores, and it will shake everything that you've ever known, ladies and gentlemen.

00:18:10.558 --> 00:18:15.872
It will change within a 24-hour period. It's going to change and it will be that quick of a change.

00:18:15.873 --> 00:18:22.691
It would be like a light switch being flipped on.'He said it would be bigger than 9/11.

00:18:22.692 --> 00:18:30.688
It's going to be such a humongous event that will change everything that quick.

00:18:30.689 --> 00:18:41.495
But He started talking to me about not being afraid. He said, 'That's not your focus. Your focus is off. You're focusing on the storm.

00:18:41.496 --> 00:19:05.482
You're focusing too much on what's coming.'He said, because I was asking Him—I was praying, you know, getting off in the flesh—and I was like, 'Oh Lord, I'm praying for the election, praying for Donald Trump, praying for this stuff, and oh God, you know what happens if the people don't get out and vote?'And I was just worrying and fretting about it.

00:19:05.483 --> 00:19:12.680
He said, 'Brandon, Brandon, Brandon, I've got this. I've got this.

00:19:12.681 --> 00:19:25.054
Like, chill, dude.'And I'm like, you know, in my heart I'm going, 'The sky is falling, I've got to pray for the nation America.'That's why He's like, 'Chill, chill, Brandon.

00:19:25.055 --> 00:19:39.638
I've got this.'Ladies and gentlemen, He's got this. The sky isn't falling even though we look at all the stuff going on around us and we think, 'Well, Lord, do you not see all the things going on?'Israel's at war.

00:19:39.639 --> 00:19:52.611
He showed me major war breaking out in Europe again. I saw a major thing happening in Europe and He told me, 'This is going to be coming, you need to pray over this.'And I prayed over it, you know, about the war escalating in Europe.

00:19:52.612 --> 00:20:08.016
And He's just warning me about these things that I'm telling you all about, but He said, 'Where is it ever to be afraid about any of it?'It's not for you to ever hide in a hole about it; it's for you to know and be prepared and warn the body so that you all can pray.

00:20:08.017 --> 00:20:12.876
And some of it, people say, 'Well, can we change it?'Some of it we can, some we can't.

00:20:12.877 --> 00:20:19.026
And I'm going to say a lot of this we probably can't because I'm telling you, He's coming.

00:20:19.027 --> 00:20:27.180
The sun is setting on this dispensation and where we are, and Jesus is getting ready to come back for His church.

00:20:27.181 --> 00:20:32.416
But I saw Adam's lease coming up. And I'll be real with y'all, I don't know where it's at in the Bible.

00:20:32.417 --> 00:20:37.909
I asked Him, 'Lord, show me,'and I've been trying to find where it talks about Adam's lease because He brought it up to me.

00:20:37.910 --> 00:20:43.470
And I said, 'Lord, where does it talk about that?'Because I'm telling you, I'm not a Bible scholar.

00:20:43.471 --> 00:21:03.519
I'm just getting these things from the Holy Spirit and I try to weigh it out with people who are educated in the Word, but I don't have a lot of people around me that are Bible scholars.

00:21:03.520 --> 00:21:21.378
But He talked to me about Adam's lease being up and I was like, 'Wow, Lord, this is interesting.'But He started talking to me about how everything was...

00:21:21.379 --> 00:21:28.035
I don't know, I'm not going to get into all that. I saw a lot about it and it was a wow.

00:21:28.036 --> 00:21:45.248
I talked to my wife about it, we talked about it, and I said, 'Babe, this is what the Lord said.'And the light was so strong when He appeared, it was so strong that it was brighter than the noonday sun at its fullest.

00:21:45.249 --> 00:21:52.430
The light that I saw when He appeared this way was so bright that I thought it was going to burn me up.

00:21:52.431 --> 00:22:09.687
And I said, 'Lord, you're going to have to turn it down or it's going to consume me.'And He took Himself behind the cliff of this thing and I could see the light—He shielded Himself with the light so that it would not burn me up in the spirit.

00:22:09.688 --> 00:22:19.340
It was so bright that it shielded, and the light was shining so bright on the other side of this shield that I could barely glimpse at it.

00:22:19.341 --> 00:22:31.402
But inside of this, this dove came out of that light and there was an olive branch in the dove's beak with the beautiful olive leaves on it.

00:22:31.403 --> 00:22:39.818
And it came out and it was flapping its wings coming out of that light, and it came over me. It was glory.

00:22:39.819 --> 00:22:49.251
And what I'm trying to tell you all—I give you bits and pieces of things—but I'm trying to tell you all a little bit of something that He showed me.

00:22:49.252 --> 00:22:56.194
And we are out of time. Jesus is coming and you better get your house in order.

00:22:56.195 --> 00:23:05.999
It's time to get bold and on fire for God like you've never seen before. It's time to arise and shine for the light has come.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:18.186
It's time for you to be serious about the Father's business, for He's coming. Are you ready for the soon return of the Lord Jesus Christ?

00:23:18.187 --> 00:23:27.886
For this dispensation of grace is coming to an end, ladies and gentlemen, and we're about to get ready to go into the seven years of tribulation.

00:23:27.887 --> 00:23:37.092
But the thousand-year reign—He has such a plan for each and every single one of you.

00:23:37.093 --> 00:23:52.454
We will see creative miracles, we will see blind eyes open, we will see dead men walk again, we will see the things that we've always desired to see.

00:23:52.455 --> 00:24:05.070
And thought, 'Is it possible?'But I'm trying to tell you all things are possible to him that believes, and a great move of the Spirit of God is right on us. It's right here.

00:24:05.071 --> 00:24:15.550
And I want my wife—she's here—to read some of the testimonies, just to stir you up, just to get you excited about what's coming, about the miracles that took place at Azusa Street.

00:24:15.551 --> 00:24:21.915
We've been reading that book, and I told her, 'Read it to me again, read it to me again.'Because faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:24:21.916 --> 00:24:25.480
And this is not the Word of God, but this is something that God did in the past.

00:24:25.481 --> 00:24:40.357
And we read the Bible, but she reads these testimonies to me to show me, 'Brandon, it's happened once and He's going to do it again.'There is a great outpouring, a great harvest of souls.

00:24:40.358 --> 00:24:59.732
I'm telling you, He's the Lord of the harvest. 'Hi everybody, I'm just reading a couple of miracles from the true stories of the miracles of Azusa Street... and there was—this is just one of the testimonies...

00:24:59.733 --> 00:25:13.193
these were just people that were there that God used to do healings and miracles.'And what we thought was cool, though, babe, was that a lot of these were young people.

00:25:13.194 --> 00:25:21.638
They were in the 18, 19, 12-year-olds—and 21-year-olds—but no, a lot of these people were not old people.

00:25:21.639 --> 00:25:28.261
They were all young people. I'm talking about being young Davids, being on fire with no fear.

00:25:28.262 --> 00:25:59.471
And I look back at what He did at Azusa, and we're reading—she's reading about—she goes, 'Brandon, another 18-year-old, another 21-year-old, another 12-year-old, another 15-year-old, 16-year-old was doing creative miracles, praying for people that needed a limb or eyes or whatever.'It wasn't like, 'Well, this guy was a seasoned veteran that was a preacher for 45 years at the Assemblies of God.'No, these were people that were just hungry, weren't they?

00:25:59.472 --> 00:26:10.333
Yeah, and it's exciting to hear these stories because you always think, 'Well, I have to be—well, I'm not a pastor, I'm not an evangelist, I can't be used.'He was using average Joes.

00:26:10.334 --> 00:26:17.519
He's going to use you. You don't have to have a platform; you don't have to have something huge.

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:23.678
Now, I'm sorry to cut you off, baby, but I'm just—I have to tell everybody, it's not somebody that has a huge church.

00:26:23.679 --> 00:26:27.532
He's going to use you, ladies and gentlemen. He's going to use you.

00:26:27.533 --> 00:26:38.473
You could just be a stay-at-home mom that's just doing homework on the weekdays with their kids and—'Hey man, I made dinner for my family'—but God's going to use you.

00:26:38.474 --> 00:26:42.374
He doesn't have to look—you don't have to have a huge church.

00:26:42.375 --> 00:26:46.398
Most of these people who have huge churches, they have egos anyway.

00:26:46.399 --> 00:26:57.545
Look at it: 'Think of the movies The Elephant Man or Mask and you can picture the total disfigurement of this 25 to 30-year-old man who came to Azusa Street.

00:26:57.546 --> 00:27:04.441
He came there on his own, pathetically dragging his feet, sickening-looking, with one eye shooting up and the other looking down.

00:27:04.442 --> 00:27:09.766
